    {
        "content": "<p>Sure. I can do this. </p>\n<p>But the new command <code>#statesearch</code> does exactly this, querying a server that is designed for accepting the goal state (and written by the same people as <code>#leansearch</code>'s server). Should we instead be advising people to use that (I don't know how stable their server is).</p>",
